| Milestone                                          | Target Date   | Dependency                              |
|---------------------------------------------------|---------------|-----------------------------------------|
| Genesis-1 ceramic factory at 30 M m²/yr           | Apr 2031      | Ceramic cladding factory                |
| First 99.9999% ceramic EUV mirror blank fired     | Q1 2032       | Genesis kiln precision upgrade          |
